description: Termine und Konzertarchiv
---

<h1 class="h1">Konzerte</h1>
<p class="lead">Termine &amp; Archiv (künftig bequem im Web-Editor pflegbar).</p>

<div class="list">
  {% set items = collections.konzert | reverse %}
  {% for post in items %}
    <div class="card">
      <h2 class="h2">{{ post.data.title }}</h2>
      <p class="muted small">{{ post.data.date }} · {{ post.data.city }} · {{ post.data.venue }}</p>
      <a class="btn" href="{{ post.url }}">Details</a>
    </div>
  {% endfor %}
</div>
